T02TD3704E:344b-1: sv'a ra sva t'i sto tra n'a ma /
T02TD3704E:344b-3: lha mo dbyangs can gyi bstod pa /
T02TD3704E:344b-4: ston zla rab rgyas ku mud dung dang chu shel gangs ri ltar dkar ba //
T02TD3704E:344b-5: rab dkar dkar gsal gzi ldan yid 'phrog lha mo dbyangs can la phyag 'tshal //
T02TD3704E:344b-6: bdag blo'i mi shes gti mug rmongs pa'i tshogs ni kun nas 'joms pa dang //
T02TD3704E:344b-7: smra ngan sun 'byin thogs med kun gzigs spobs pa'i gter mchog rgyas par mdzod //
T02TD3704E:344b-8: sgrib gnyis sprin bral blo gros 'od zer stong ldan rab tu 'char ka yi //
T02TD3704E:344b-9: nyi ma'i zer gyis gdul bya'i padmo rab dul kha 'byed rnam rgyas pas //
T02TD3704E:344b-10: rab tu dri zhim bsil ngad dang ldan padmo'i ze'u 'bru'i ngos dag la //
T02TD3704E:344b-11: bdag blos gus pas 'thungs pas blo gros cher rgyas sbrang rtsis 'gro rnams skyong //
T02TD3704E:344b-12: gser gyi ri dang kun mkhyen chu gter lta bur kun nas lhun chags pa //
T02TD3704E:344b-13: rtsod pa'i phye ma leb dang /
T02TD3704E:344b-14: bdud sde dus kyi rlung gis bskyod ma yin //
T02TD3704E:344b-15: bcu drug na tshod lta bu'i bu mo rab mdzes sgeg pa'i nyams dang ldan //
T02TD3704E:344b-16: lha yi rgyan rnams du mas khyod kyi lus dang yan lag mdzes pa yis //
T02TD3704E:345a-0: chu gter 'gram gnas mgrin sngon dga' bskyed rgya mtsho'i lha mo dbyangs @345a * //
T02TD3704E:345a-2: khyod la phyag 'tshal brtse bas bdag blo'i mi shes mun pa myur du gsol //
T02TD3704E:345a-3: rab tu snyan pa'i dbyangs ldan dri za'i bu mo rab mdzes yid 'phrog ma //
T02TD3704E:345a-4: lag gi 'du byed rab tu bsgyur bas tshangs pa'i gsung dbyangs rnam 'byung bas //
T02TD3704E:345a-5: sgra dang tshad ma snyan dngags mngon brjod sdeb sbyor legs bshad chos rnams kun //
T02TD3704E:345a-6: pha rol yid 'phrog 'dzin par nus pa ci phyir bdag la mi stsol lags //
T02TD3704E:345a-7: khyod kyi thugs ni kun du mi g-yo rgya mtsho chen po lta bu ste //
T02TD3704E:345a-8: thugs rje'i rlabs shugs drag tu bskyed pas 'gro ba'i gdung ba rab tu sol //
T02TD3704E:345a-9: dbang gi rgyal po'i 'byung gnas yid bzhin re skong dbyangs can rgya mtsho yis //
T02TD3704E:345a-10: rmongs pa'i gdung bas gdungs pa'i skye bo rings par skyong ba dang //
T02TD3704E:345a-11: gti mug dag gis blo dman skye bo'i re ba myur du skongs //
T02TD3704E:345a-12: bdag blo'i ku mu da ni rab du kha zums rnam par gnag pa la //
T02TD3704E:345a-13: bsil zer byed pa rab tu sprin bral dkyil 'khor rnam par rgyas pa yis //
T02TD3704E:345a-14: ku mud kha bye rab rgyas ze'u 'bru yi bsil dngar rnam par spel bar mdzod //
T02TD3704E:345a-15: rab tu dri bral rkyen gyi dri mas ma phog ma 'gags khyod kyi sku //
T02TD3704E:345a-16: kun du tshangs pa'i dbyangs can ca co'i dri bral khyod kyi gsung //
T02TD3704E:345a-17: shes bya kun la thogs pa med pa'i ye shes dang ldan khyod kyi thugs //
T02TD3704E:345a-18: bstod pa 'di yis bstod la dbyangs can ma yis blo gros mchog rab stsol //
T02TD3704E:345a-19: dbyangs can gyi bstod pa 'di ni /
T02TD3704E:345a-20: lho phyogs kyi rgyud du byung ba'i mkhas pa chen po pandi ta nag mo'i khol gyis dbyangs can zhal gzigs pa'i dus su dgyes te bstod pa rdzogs so /
T02TD3704E:345a-22: // / gang zhig 'di 'don pa la shes rab stsol bar khas blangs so ;
T02TD3704E:345a-23: / rgya gar gyi mkhan po panti ta dzny'a na sh'i la dang /
T02TD3704E:345a-24: lo ts'a ba dge slong chos 'bar gyis bsgyur ba'o /
